| Protocol Name   | Description                                               |   Deprecation Release |   Scheduled Removal Release | Replacement   |
|:----------------|:----------------------------------------------------------|----------------------:|----------------------------:|:--------------|
| SSL             | Used to create a secure, encrypted connection to MongoDB. |                2023.2 |                      2024.2 | TLS           |
